OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry throughout the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Clear skies at first, but
OL,8,Fhigh cloud spreading in from the west
OL,9,Flater. Overnight frost developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start with
OL,12,Fovernight frost it will be another dry
OL,13,Fand bright day with some sunny spells,
OL,14,Fthough some western areas starting
OL,15,Fcloudier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
