OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,7,FMonday, often dry but with the
OL,8,Foccasional spell of rain. Dry start
OL,9,FTuesday but becoming windier as rain
OL,10,Fspreads east later.
